title: App/phone to control use
comment: This means the implant is easy to use but may have negative consequences - somebody using your phone can control your body, hacking, technical issues, etc

title: Self -sustaining and repairing
comment: Self-sustains using available substances in the body, can perform it's own minor repairs

title: Minimally invasive
comment: Because the implant doesn't require maintenance, can perform minor repairs by itself,  and lasts up to 20 years it's about as non-invasive as a technological implant could be

title: Long-lasting
comment: Contributes to the implant being as non-invasive as possible
